title: FeatherEx 10 Pack Premier Shipping Boxes
features: One FeatherEx Premier Box: 18" long x 10" wide x 19" true height. Total weight must not exceed: 10 lbs
Box comes glued and ‘Ready To Go’. APPROVED BY USPS. Light weight and durable. Made in the USA. Can assemble in 10 sec.
Better ventilation - Air-vents glued with bio-filter fabric. Comes with diagonal divider and bottom insert piece
Shipping is available to AK, HI & PR via USPS Standard Post.
Inspection viewing window for official use to see the condition of the birds. Equipped with Tie holes and Easy-to-carry handle.Wider than our competitor’s box.
description: This includes divider. This divider allows you to make two compartments with inside the box. There are two holes on this box handle to feed twine for tying multiple boxes together. Three boxes tied together makes the largest box you can ship through USPS. Size of this Premier Box: 18" long x 10" wide x 19" true height..... Total weight must not exceed: 10 lbs..... Weight empty: approx. 1 lb, 12 oz..... Good for one to many birds depending on the size of your bird..... For eg...... Ducks - Teal and other small ducks - many, Large duck like Eider - 1..... ..... Pheasants - Adult size eared pheasant - 1, Impeyan pheasant - 1, Temminck's Tragopan - 1, Golden pheasants - 2 with a divider...... Others - Pigeons - 4 to 6, Old English Bantams - 1, Larger Game Bird - 1,Few passeriformes (Canaries & Finches). Shipping is available to anywhere in the lower 48 states via FedEx.
